  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the creator of the Piczle series comes the latest nonogram experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/5e80fbc1f42adc934ef5501327dfcc9b.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/a31c723d633e4fc91c2ebf1561d30900.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=172 /></span>300 nonogram puzzles with both classic and color variations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/e909c7309d3849000ebd06c0f7279877.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=172 /></span>20 collage puzzles, made up of many smaller puzzles, both in classic and color variations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/eceffd0620714139097ff9af1a395677.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/5a3a6c04b146fb882f4672645ceb4c31.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=172 /></span>Unlock entries in the in-game Bestiary and learn more about the beasts of Rigbarth!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/fa6f9b9d4bdae76df2f0f2456bd47177.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/dbe731275e2142e6135cef679a5f7bdd.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=172 /></span>Unlock entries in the in-game Compendium and learn about the characters in Rune Factory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/0f2d83f68eaaf9aa706d36dabbd3575f.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/ac40c72121740437933f9627b4d60224.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=172 /></span>Customise your farm, pick your spouse and choose your weapons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/fe674e5f169b10caa1b91895fc0bee2c.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=68 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/016539b3e4a41b82357e53d8cbb12242.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=172 /></span>Play how you want: laid-back and relaxed or challenging! <br>A wealth of puzzle options to tweak the experience to your exact liking! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134280/extras/2dda34cb2b8d7a32da0007779b04e68f.avif?t=1745451886\" width=616 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself, ...or don't! There is no wrong way to play!</p>",
